We recommend installing PDAL and the PDAL Python extension in an environment other than the base environment
pdal: will install the PDAL binaries and development files.
python-pdal: will install the PDAL Python extension.

install in new env:
 - conda create --yes --name <myenv> --channel conda-forge pdal python-pdal gdal

install in existing env:
 - conda install --name <myenv> --channel conda-forge pdal python-pdal gdal


ref: https://pdal.io/quickstart.html



